ActCanada Disability Savings Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Honourable Kent Hehr to be "the Minister" for the purposes of the Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing the P.C. 2017-78 of February 1, 2017; and (2) designating the Honourable Kent Hehr, a minister of the Crown, as the Minister for the purposes of the Canada Disability Savings Act.
